      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "redis主从架构搭建，配置从节点步骤：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "PTCjUn3T9PVw9SFmZcHis",
      "originalText": "redis主从架构搭建，配置从节点步骤：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0flfQ_L8j7ngk3WDpqSq7",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -2467.2354318451967,
      "y": 4682.391056826352,
      "width": 928,
      "height": 610,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "cun2dr_wP2yObGANILt5C"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHYJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1441864572,
      "version": 189,
      "versionNonce": 823100594,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "l-wTlt8zjrZh9XUIQ21Gl",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "l-wTlt8zjrZh9XUIQ21Gl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2462.2354318451967,
      "y": 4687.391056826352,
      "width": 900.6998291015625,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "cun2dr_wP2yObGANILt5C"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHYK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 358340292,
      "version": 352,
      "versionNonce": 1293801326,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1、复制一份redis.conf文件\n\n2、将相关配置修改为如下值：\nport 6380\npidfile /var/run/redis_6380.pid # 把pid进程号写入pidfile配置的文件\nlogfile \"6380.log\"\ndir /usr/local/redis‐5.0.3/data/6380 # 指定数据存放目录\n# 需要注释掉bind\n# bind 127.0.0.1（bind绑定的是自己机器网卡的ip，如果有多块网卡可以配多个ip，代表允许客户端通\n过机器的哪些网卡ip去访问，内网一般可以不配置bind，注释掉即可）\n\n3、配置主从复制\nreplicaof 192.168.0.60 6379 # 从本机6379的redis实例复制数据，Redis 5.0之前使用slaveof\nreplica‐read‐only yes # 配置从节点只读\n\n4、启动从节点\nredis‐server redis.conf\n\n5、连接从节点\nredis‐cli ‐p 6380\n\n6、测试在6379实例上写数据，6380实例是否能及时同步新修改数据\n\n7、可以自己再配置一个6381的从节点",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "0flfQ_L8j7ngk3WDpqSq7",
      "originalText": "1、复制一份redis.conf文件\n\n2、将相关配置修改为如下值：\nport 6380\npidfile /var/run/redis_6380.pid # 把pid进程号写入pidfile配置的文件\nlogfile \"6380.log\"\ndir /usr/local/redis‐5.0.3/data/6380 # 指定数据存放目录\n# 需要注释掉bind\n# bind 127.0.0.1（bind绑定的是自己机器网卡的ip，如果有多块网卡可以配多个ip，代表允许客户端通\n过机器的哪些网卡ip去访问，内网一般可以不配置bind，注释掉即可）\n\n3、配置主从复制\nreplicaof 192.168.0.60 6379 # 从本机6379的redis实例复制数据，Redis 5.0之前使用slaveof\nreplica‐read‐only yes # 配置从节点只读\n\n4、启动从节点\nredis‐server redis.conf\n\n5、连接从节点\nredis‐cli ‐p 6380\n\n6、测试在6379实例上写数据，6380实例是否能及时同步新修改数据\n\n7、可以自己再配置一个6381的从节点",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
