      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "AOF文件里可能有太多没用指令，所以AOF会定期根据内存的最新数据生成aof文件",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "W3I4EaA099WG3fLQAbcJt",
      "originalText": "AOF文件里可能有太多没用指令，所以AOF会定期根据内存的最新数据生成aof文件",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
