    {
      "id": "sK5Ha43aASVHgT5fOfqyz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -122.72721412307794,
      "y": 3630.287307444917,
      "width": 655.4798583984375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHa9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 477156348,
      "version": 592,
      "versionNonce": 1100783730,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "bgsave 子进程是由主线程 fork 生成的，可以共享主线程的所有内存数据。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "3DMonHeK6DODKw_0IzZZA",
      "originalText": "bgsave 子进程是由主线程 fork 生成的，可以共享主线程的所有内存数据。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FRa8qVzPfl8_IycZwHevs",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -129.29901733613235,
      "y": 3666.4528362475066,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaA",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 741891452,
      "version": 270,
      "versionNonce": 743528366,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "2GgYIUbJKOWOALuOLl9DX",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "2GgYIUbJKOWOALuOLl9DX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -120.43894043183548,
      "y": 3671.4528362475066,
      "width": 702.2798461914062,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1051949508,
      "version": 522,
      "versionNonce": 2111029810,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "bgsave 子进程运行后，开始读取主线程的内存数据，并把它们写入 RDB 文件。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "FRa8qVzPfl8_IycZwHevs",
      "originalText": "bgsave 子进程运行后，开始读取主线程的内存数据，并把它们写入 RDB 文件。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Bd6Fx25P05JBo-ssVlcz3",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -129.29901733613235,
      "y": 3707.6183650500966,
      "width": 814,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaC",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1690783228,
      "version": 271,
      "versionNonce": 1273377262,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "3XvElrlAYLsSMnn5SEo1M",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "3XvElrlAYLsSMnn5SEo1M",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -119.83893432831985,
      "y": 3712.6183650500966,
      "width": 795.079833984375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1403843708,
      "version": 420,
      "versionNonce": 1916840946,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "此时，如果主线程对这些数据也都是读操作，那么，主线程和 bgsave 子进程相互不影响。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Bd6Fx25P05JBo-ssVlcz3",
      "originalText": "此时，如果主线程对这些数据也都是读操作，那么，主线程和 bgsave 子进程相互不影响。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eAAKpbTBOZT3jyuUpUfEl",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -129.29901733613235,
      "y": 3748.783893852686,
      "width": 950,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#96f2d7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaE",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 2133077628,
      "version": 284,
      "versionNonce": 1348846638,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "oAIXi9K3cSzcM56x3MrkD",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "oAIXi9K3cSzcM56x3MrkD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -124.29901733613235,
      "y": 3753.783893852686,
      "width": 940,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1MRlShqNiqsFaSeo-lgMR",
        "32kSgWzUOQ7QUC2Io9-ev"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHaF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1093116228,
      "version": 556,
      "versionNonce": 1450858094,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147257345,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "但是，如果主线程要修改一块数据，那么，这块数据就会被复制一份，生成该数据的副本。然后，主线程在\n副本上修改数据，bgsave子进程会把原数据写入rdb。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "eAAKpbTBOZT3jyuUpUfEl",
      "originalText": "但是，如果主线程要修改一块数据，那么，这块数据就会被复制一份，生成该数据的副本。然后，主线程在副本上修改数据，bgsave子进程会把原数据写入rdb。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
