      "text": "主从复制(部分复制，断点续传)流程图：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "dXwR9baQ2YW-M29K_3Z58",
      "originalText": "主从复制(部分复制，断点续传)流程图：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BPqAhB7HdS-gl02IxURQq",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 2359.5509505135788,
      "y": 7794.743570551925,
      "width": 824,
      "height": 502,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QbN6kFfFqKodQsg3WkUL_",
        "yB0j75WSkR9AkqaNWy7nt"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHb9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1974304892,
      "version": 644,
      "versionNonce": 1526922930,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "24739866e001783c4cbc9ff83ab4fb8b00a2a264",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "cK7rd0ry3GlXmAe4Isuvr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2359.5509505135788,
      "y": 7584.929369425207,
      "width": 1037.591508937669,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#eebefa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QbN6kFfFqKodQsg3WkUL_",
        "yB0j75WSkR9AkqaNWy7nt"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1667928828,
      "version": 462,
      "versionNonce": 162987374,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "当master和slave断开重连后，一般都会对整份数据进行复制。但从redis2.8版本开始，redis改用可以支持部分数据复\n制的命令PSYNC去master同步数据，slave与master能够在网络连接断开重连后只进行部分数据复制(断点续传)。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "当master和slave断开重连后，一般都会对整份数据进行复制。但从redis2.8版本开始，redis改用可以支持部分数据复制的命令PSYNC去master同步数据，slave与master能够在网络连接断开重连后只进行部分数据复制(断点续传)。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xH06hB0ggS3pRw68UNPJE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2359.5509505135788,
      "y": 7646.534103134113,
      "width": 1111.4141950062622,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#eebefa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QbN6kFfFqKodQsg3WkUL_",
        "yB0j75WSkR9AkqaNWy7nt"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1283009220,
      "version": 480,
      "versionNonce": 1330927730,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "master会在其内存中创建一个复制数据用的缓存队列，缓存最近一段时间的数据，master和它所有的slave都维护了复制的数\n据下标offset和master的进程id，因此，当网络连接断开后，slave会请求master继续进行未完成的复制，从所记录的数据下标\n开始。如果master进程id变化了，或者从节点数据下标offset太旧，已经不在master的缓存队列里了，那么将会进行一次全量\n数据的复制。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "master会在其内存中创建一个复制数据用的缓存队列，缓存最近一段时间的数据，master和它所有的slave都维护了复制的数据下标offset和master的进程id，因此，当网络连接断开后，slave会请求master继续进行未完成的复制，从所记录的数据下标开始。如果master进程id变化了，或者从节点数据下标offset太旧，已经不在master的缓存队列里了，那么将会进行一次全量数据的复制。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
