    {
      "id": "uFWSdkZM1SehSZecMQBXF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2375.038466668668,
      "y": 7118.035550042268,
      "width": 974.688690343601,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dikiLypxP5ezNF-FiKQq4",
        "yB0j75WSkR9AkqaNWy7nt"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1377992516,
      "version": 581,
      "versionNonce": 1809087026,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果有很多从节点，为了缓解主从复制风暴(多个从节点同时复制主节点导致主节点压力过大)，可以做如下架\n构，让部分从节点与从节点(与主节点同步)同步数据",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果有很多从节点，为了缓解主从复制风暴(多个从节点同时复制主节点导致主节点压力过大)，可以做如下架构，让部分从节点与从节点(与主节点同步)同步数据",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
