      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Redis Lua脚本",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Uavih0V3qaJ-WxOceWnYg",
      "originalText": "Redis Lua脚本",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DfwCz3b1kzknv7q2SZ5KL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8353.482157565255,
      "width": 396.4794921875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 408820548,
      "version": 561,
      "versionNonce": 680841522,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "EVAL script numkeys key [key ...] arg [arg ...]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "EVAL script numkeys key [key ...] arg [arg ...]",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DikOID37WytCFStrtNKtK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 9360.224250473539,
      "width": 1244.9199218749998,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 272233468,
      "version": 525,
      "versionNonce": 1958843118,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "注意，不要在Lua脚本中出现死循环和耗时的运算，否则redis会阻塞，将不接受其他的命令， 所以使用时要注意不能出现死循环、耗时的运\n算。redis是单进程、单线程执行脚本。管道不会阻塞redis。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "注意，不要在Lua脚本中出现死循环和耗时的运算，否则redis会阻塞，将不接受其他的命令， 所以使用时要注意不能出现死循环、耗时的运算。redis是单进程、单线程执行脚本。管道不会阻塞redis。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aQgfG_zDS_9rH9La5NlCG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8195.90145992916,
      "width": 1459.97998046875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 478061436,
      "version": 463,
      "versionNonce": 1611127538,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Redis在2.6推出了脚本功能，允许开发者使用Lua语言编写脚本传到Redis中执行。使用脚本的好处如下:\n1、减少网络开销：本来5次网络请求的操作，可以用一个请求完成，原先5次请求的逻辑放在redis服务器上完成。使用脚本，减少了网络往返时延。这点跟管道类似。\n2、原子操作：Redis会将整个脚本作为一个整体执行，中间不会被其他命令插入。管道不是原子的，不过redis的批量操作命令(类似mset)是原子的。\n3、替代redis的事务功能：redis自带的事务功能很鸡肋，而redis的lua脚本几乎实现了常规的事务功能，官方推荐如果要使用redis的事务功能可以用redis lua替代。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Redis在2.6推出了脚本功能，允许开发者使用Lua语言编写脚本传到Redis中执行。使用脚本的好处如下:\n1、减少网络开销：本来5次网络请求的操作，可以用一个请求完成，原先5次请求的逻辑放在redis服务器上完成。使用脚本，减少了网络往返时延。这点跟管道类似。\n2、原子操作：Redis会将整个脚本作为一个整体执行，中间不会被其他命令插入。管道不是原子的，不过redis的批量操作命令(类似mset)是原子的。\n3、替代redis的事务功能：redis自带的事务功能很鸡肋，而redis的lua脚本几乎实现了常规的事务功能，官方推荐如果要使用redis的事务功能可以用redis lua替代。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c2jtggsKIBQp2HFaWOn-K",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8312.191808747208,
      "width": 790.7798461914062,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1947837892,
      "version": 491,
      "versionNonce": 1764558126,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "从Redis2.6.0版本开始，通过内置的Lua解释器，可以使用EVAL命令对Lua脚本进行求值。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "从Redis2.6.0版本开始，通过内置的Lua解释器，可以使用EVAL命令对Lua脚本进行求值。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vdMrSQEkFwnTExzl34mKW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8394.772506383302,
      "width": 1029.0798339843748,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1787752060,
      "version": 528,
      "versionNonce": 1341369522,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "script参数是一段Lua脚本程序，它会被运行在Redis服务器上下文中，这段脚本不必(也不应该)定义为一个Lua函数。\nnumkeys参数用于指定键名参数的个数。键名参数 key [key ...] 从EVAL的第三个参数开始算起，表示在脚本中所用到\n的那些Redis键(key)，这些键名参数可以在 Lua中通过全局变量KEYS数组，用1为基址的形式访问( KEYS[1] ，\nKEYS[2] ，以此类推)。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "script参数是一段Lua脚本程序，它会被运行在Redis服务器上下文中，这段脚本不必(也不应该)定义为一个Lua函数。numkeys参数用于指定键名参数的个数。键名参数 key [key ...] 从EVAL的第三个参数开始算起，表示在脚本中所用到的那些Redis键(key)，这些键名参数可以在 Lua中通过全局变量KEYS数组，用1为基址的形式访问( KEYS[1] ， KEYS[2] ，以此类推)。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4CDLnOo0FpboEsbjukSMq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8511.06285520135,
      "width": 1026.8596191406248,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2096777028,
      "version": 582,
      "versionNonce": 468725614,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在命令的最后，那些不是键名参数的附加参数 arg [arg ...] ，可以在Lua中通过全局变量ARGV数组访问，访问的形式\n和KEYS变量类似( ARGV[1] 、 ARGV[2] ，诸如此类)。例如",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在命令的最后，那些不是键名参数的附加参数 arg [arg ...] ，可以在Lua中通过全局变量ARGV数组访问，访问的形式和KEYS变量类似( ARGV[1] 、 ARGV[2] ，诸如此类)。例如",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CS5XW3zaTx68rjbnEFoqm",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8577.353204019397,
      "width": 1038,
      "height": 198,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 578291324,
      "version": 465,
      "versionNonce": 2113881714,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "dc7452581f5933a6f29a8f4a16027fee3105633b",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "xhhk5UlWtoADtGpHUvW10",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4001.211838574074,
      "y": 8791.643552837444,
      "width": 1212.1761127236045,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dxD4jF70BICTA9QmP7PpP",
        "FGIklQk-1AmKxsUP6OHQp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1187443964,
      "version": 661,
      "versionNonce": 1498681774,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "其中 \"return {KEYS[1],KEYS[2],ARGV[1],ARGV[2]}\" 是被求值的Lua脚本，数字2指定了键名参数的数量， key1和key2是键名参数，分别\n使用 KEYS[1] 和 KEYS[2] 访问，而最后的 first 和 second 则是附加参数，可以通过 ARGV[1] 和 ARGV[2] 访问它们。\n在 Lua 脚本中，可以使用redis.call()函数来执行Redis命令\nJedis调用示例详见上面jedis连接示例：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "其中 \"return {KEYS[1],KEYS[2],ARGV[1],ARGV[2]}\" 是被求值的Lua脚本，数字2指定了键名参数的数量， key1和key2是键名参数，分别使用 KEYS[1] 和 KEYS[2] 访问，而最后的 first 和 second 则是附加参数，可以通过 ARGV[1] 和 ARGV[2] 访问它们。\n在 Lua 脚本中，可以使用redis.call()函数来执行Redis命令\nJedis调用示例详见上面jedis连接示例：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "16O04ff8yIYj4xOuUZ3jO",
