      "text": "redis哨兵架构搭建步骤：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "7LUi1RD1GmcNMvnP-xh1r",
      "originalText": "redis哨兵架构搭建步骤：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c1cH7w8WBDIJcivw2HolD",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -2113.553242119658,
      "y": 7493.9107552772275,
      "width": 1112,
      "height": 560,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "j_u5g_cHDPKuXDFowjCGV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbf",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1054529356,
      "version": 358,
      "versionNonce": 1725323954,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "3pu2oL-nWtewHy1ppKR6N",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "3pu2oL-nWtewHy1ppKR6N",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2108.553242119658,
      "y": 7498.9107552772275,
      "width": 1101.4794921875,
      "height": 550,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "j_u5g_cHDPKuXDFowjCGV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbg",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1025998540,
      "version": 421,
      "versionNonce": 1549230446,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1、复制一份sentinel.conf文件\ncp sentinel.conf sentinel-26379.conf\n\n2、将相关配置修改为如下值：\nport 26379\ndaemonize yes\npidfile \"/var/run/redis-sentinel-26379.pid\"\nlogfile \"26379.log\"\ndir \"/usr/local/redis-5.0.3/data\"\n# sentinel monitor <master-redis-name> <master-redis-ip> <master-redis-port> <quorum>\n# quorum是一个数字，指明当有多少个sentinel认为一个master失效时(值一般为：sentinel总数/2 + 1)，master才算真正失效\nsentinel monitor mymaster 192.168.0.60 6379 2   # mymaster这个名字随便取，客户端访问时会用到\n\n3、启动sentinel哨兵实例\nsrc/redis-sentinel sentinel-26379.conf\n\n4、查看sentinel的info信息\nsrc/redis-cli -p 26379\n127.0.0.1:26379>info\n可以看到Sentinel的info里已经识别出了redis的主从\n\n5、可以自己再配置两个sentinel，端口26380和26381，注意上述配置文件里的对应数字都要修改",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "c1cH7w8WBDIJcivw2HolD",
      "originalText": "1、复制一份sentinel.conf文件\ncp sentinel.conf sentinel-26379.conf\n\n2、将相关配置修改为如下值：\nport 26379\ndaemonize yes\npidfile \"/var/run/redis-sentinel-26379.pid\"\nlogfile \"26379.log\"\ndir \"/usr/local/redis-5.0.3/data\"\n# sentinel monitor <master-redis-name> <master-redis-ip> <master-redis-port> <quorum>\n# quorum是一个数字，指明当有多少个sentinel认为一个master失效时(值一般为：sentinel总数/2 + 1)，master才算真正失效\nsentinel monitor mymaster 192.168.0.60 6379 2   # mymaster这个名字随便取，客户端访问时会用到\n\n3、启动sentinel哨兵实例\nsrc/redis-sentinel sentinel-26379.conf\n\n4、查看sentinel的info信息\nsrc/redis-cli -p 26379\n127.0.0.1:26379>info\n可以看到Sentinel的info里已经识别出了redis的主从\n\n5、可以自己再配置两个sentinel，端口26380和26381，注意上述配置文件里的对应数字都要修改",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q7VhvwVk7n5-s7CK6wAiT",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1333.1818181818185,
      "y": 9746.320802657889,
      "width": 1531,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbh",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1131547340,
      "version": 167,
      "versionNonce": 1079784562,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "crVoGHMLYDuELAFdMFw0y",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "crVoGHMLYDuELAFdMFw0y",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1338.1818181818185,
      "y": 9751.320802657889,
      "width": 1520.1597900390625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1491159116,
      "version": 171,
      "versionNonce": 704971694,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "sentinel集群都启动完毕后，会将哨兵集群的元数据信息写入所有sentinel的配置文件里去(追加在文件的最下面)，我们查看下如下配置文件sentinel-26379.conf，如下所示：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Q7VhvwVk7n5-s7CK6wAiT",
      "originalText": "sentinel集群都启动完毕后，会将哨兵集群的元数据信息写入所有sentinel的配置文件里去(追加在文件的最下面)，我们查看下如下配置文件sentinel-26379.conf，如下所示：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "whjzAv-2vmPqLyXgns0wa",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 1333.1818181818185,
      "y": 9792.208345764942,
      "width": 1371,
      "height": 149,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
