      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbk",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1729883724,
      "version": 489,
      "versionNonce": 776232430,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "QGxtfRC5vAEMm-JHmeG16",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "QGxtfRC5vAEMm-JHmeG16",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1338.1818181818185,
      "y": 9957.095888871996,
      "width": 1351.9197998046875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHbl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1613483252,
      "version": 228,
      "versionNonce": 220938226,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773147118414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "当redis主节点如果挂了，哨兵集群会重新选举出新的redis主节点，同时会修改所有sentinel节点配置文件的集群元数据信息，比如6379的redis如果挂了，\n假设选举出的新主节点是6380，则sentinel文件里的集群元数据信息会变成如下所示：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "BrzmEdfxpO0nrTAu-oe8T",
      "originalText": "当redis主节点如果挂了，哨兵集群会重新选举出新的redis主节点，同时会修改所有sentinel节点配置文件的集群元数据信息，比如6379的redis如果挂了，假设选举出的新主节点是6380，则sentinel文件里的集群元数据信息会变成如下所示：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pXGx2XnENYjF6K9knhjMW",
      "type": "image",
